		"description": "Complete test collection for the Warehouse Inventory Reservation API.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set the `baseUrl` collection variable (default: http://localhost:8080)\n3. Set the `apiKey` collection variable (default: dev-key-12345)\n4. Run requests individually or use the Collection Runner\n\n## Folders\n- **Happy Path** — All successful request scenarios\n- **Negative Scenarios** — Error & edge-case testing",
